This year of the Ox is filled with $10M lai-see and joy!
- CNY special referral programme (starting 9/2) 
- New lai-see function (starting 10/2) 
- Limited-time CNY quest (starting 10/2) 
More, starting from 8 Feb 2021, you’ll receive App notification for high-risk transactions. Find out more in the ZA Bank App and the email we sent you earlier.
